{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2929","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2929/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2929/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2929/events","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2929","id":13189090,"number":2929,"title":"allow symlink core files from document root","user":{"login":"kzoli","id":4158269,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/484bf15e568d0c809e570371cc8e964f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fae864bcfd15a2ba6a099970bae364439.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"484bf15e568d0c809e570371cc8e964f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli","html_url":"https://github.com/kzoli","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kzoli/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","assignee":null,"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2013-04-15t08:21:01z","updated_at":"2013-04-17t10:43:10z","closed_at":"2013-04-17t10:43:10z","pull_request":{"html_url":null,"diff_url":null,"patch_url":null},"body":"admins running multiple oc instances on a webserver maybe want to symlink a common oc core without duplicating them. moving core into a r/o filesystem (for example /usr/share or /usr/local/share in debian) maybe a security hardening also (downside is losing automatic update feature). using php realpath and (__dir__) constant in /lib/base.php blocks symlinking. \r\n\r\ntwo simple modifications:\r\n<pre>                // calculate the root directories\r\n-               oc::$serverroot = str_replace(\"\\\\\", '/', substr(__dir__, 0, -4));\r\n+               oc::$serverroot = str_replace(\"\\\\\",'/',$_server['document_root']);\r\n</pre>\r\n<pre>\r\n-               oc::$suburi = str_replace(\"\\\\\", \"/\", substr(realpath($_server[\"script_filename\"]), strlen(oc::$serverroot)));\r\n+               oc::$suburi = substr($_server[\"script_filename\"],strlen(oc::$serverroot));\r\n</pre>\r\nresolves problem on debian wheezy and oc 5.0.4. can i propose modifying base.php.\r\n\r\n[sorry about my terrible english...]","closed_by":{"login":"raydiation","id":195053,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/aa0d7b7302e0d7f4f9513c23b571383a?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2faf0a25e27510f77d97634a6bbe653b13.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"aa0d7b7302e0d7f4f9513c23b571383a","url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation","html_url":"https://github.com/raydiation","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/raydiation/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}